isualise an AP graphically. вАҐ Identify Geometric Progressions (GP). вАҐ Determine the nth term of a GP. вАҐ Visualise a GP graphically. вАҐ Analyse attributes of fractals using GP. вАҐ Solve the Tower of Hanoi puzzle. вАҐ Use computational thinking to identify patterns, write step-by-step rules, and model patterns in sequences and progressions.

