xamples on parallel lines CG-7, C-7.1, C-7.3, CG-9 The student will be able to: вАҐ Explain the notion of an angle. вАҐ Explain the notion of a ray. вАҐ Explain that angles are formed between two rays with a common starting point. вАҐ State that a straight angle equals two right angles and measures 180¬∞ while a right angle measures 90¬∞.

